 "近日，全国政协委员，首都经济贸易大学文化与传播学院副院长郭媛媛在接受中新社采访时表示，游戏产业属于文化产业的一部分，不仅要能满足人民群众丰富的需要，生产的游戏还应具有一定社会责任感。郭媛媛表示，平衡未成年人保护与游戏产业高质量发展，应讲究「精品」、「精准」两个「精」。精品是指提供给未成年人的游戏应当是分层、分级、分类，具有针对未成年人成长的精制的产品内容；精准则指的是游戏要根据不同年龄，不同阶段的孩子的成长需要进行分类提供。（记者 宋宇晟） 【两会 30 秒】郭媛媛委员：平衡未成年人保护与游戏产业高质量发展 应讲究两个「精」"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/588270406"}}, "attached_info": "ClQI/NSI0dien89cEAMaCDkzMDA4NTM1IKjGoKAGMAA4EkAncgk1ODgyNzA0MDZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1678322760.7842357", "card_id": "Q_565062536", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 878}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么人到绝境后会大彻大悟？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-9931035fb75f15b0220ac4b6022c488a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/565062536"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/NSI0dien89cEAMaCDg3ODUxNDMzIKXUn5sGMAk42RZAKHIJNTY1MDYyNTM2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_1678322760.7847605", "card_id": "Q_585929021", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "10 公里跑在跑者心中的地位有多重要？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-564d82ba7e876e77d46c87bb0f947b9e_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/585929021"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I/NSI0dien89cEAMaCDkyNDg4MjE2IOn